Hanover, made personal donations to national, state and city chapters of Planned Parenthood totaling $900 in 1993,
1994, 1998 and 1999." (The Politico)

* "Forget President Bloomberg"... NYC Mayor Michael Bloomberg "who'll be forced to leave office when his term expires
in less than three years, is eyeing a run for governor against Eliot Spitzer in 2010." (New York Post)

