* Sen. John McCain (R-AZ) attends town halls in Council Bluffs (9:45 am ET) and Fort Dodge, IA (12:30 pm ET).  Tonight,
McCain fundraises in Gross Pointe, MI.

* Attorney General Alberto Gonzales speaks about "Enhancing & Securing Civil Liberties of all Americans" at the Detroit
Economic Club at 12 pm ET.

